		<div class="comment-author vcard">
			<img alt='' src='http://1.gravatar.com/avatar/36a713761072924e678e7d4223e41edc?s=48&amp;d=identicon&amp;r=G' class='avatar avatar-48 photo' height='48' width='48' />
			<cite class="fn">Kim</cite>

